<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Shayak Partner</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4A90E2;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .steps {
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .step {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 15px;
      border-left: 3px solid #4A90E2;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4A90E2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Shayak Partner!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining Shayak Partner! We're excited to have you on board as a service professional.</p>
      
      <p>You're just a few steps away from offering your services to customers in your area:</p>
      
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h3>1. Complete Your Profile</h3>
          <p>Add your personal details and professional information.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <h3>2. Select Your Services</h3>
          <p>Choose the services you're qualified to provide<% if (specializations && specializations.length > 0) { %> (you've already selected <%= specializations %>)<% } %>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <h3>3. Upload Documents</h3>
          <p>Submit your ID proof, address proof, and professional certifications for verification.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <h3>4. Get Verified</h3>
          <p>Once your documents are verified, you can start accepting service requests!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p>Our team is here to help you succeed. If you have any questions, please reach out to our support team.</p>
      
      <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Open App</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Shayak Partner. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>You received this email because you signed up for a Shayak Partner account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>